{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"289e0c9477","title":"对李克农病况报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ac599d02cb","index":0,"year":1953,"month":3,"day":4,"articleId":"289e0c9477"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji33","name":"毛泽东全集第33卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/33-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji33":{"comments":[{"id":"8460d3afd1","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"289e0c9477","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这个批语写在中央人民政府卫生部副部长傅连障1953年2月21日关于外交部副部长李克农的病况给周恩来的报告上。报告说，李克农自1943年起，即有发作性心前区疼痛症状，每年发作一二次。去年则加重了，每月发作五六次。今年返京后，每天都发作，昨晚并曾晕倒，管迷了五六分钟才清醒。今早苏联大夫和黄树则同志会诊，诊断为“冠状动脉硬化”及“过度疲劳”，建议到医院检查治疗，李克农尚未同意。安眠药平常服量为0.2毫克，他竞服过0.8毫克，我已再三劝他不能这样用，如此用下去有中毒的危险。"},{"id":"e81bd90664","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"289e0c9477","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"尚昆，即杨尚昆，当时任中共中央办公厅主任。"}],"contents":[{"id":"4f476016a2","type":"title","text":"对李克农病况报告的批语则","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"289e0c9477"},{"id":"8460d3afd1","type":"paragraph","text":"尚昆同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"289e0c9477"},{"id":"e81bd90664","type":"paragraph","text":"克农这样对自己病状的处理是很危险的，请你劝他遵医幅休养，并决不可那样服药法。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"289e0c9477"},{"id":"4faf6f5875","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"289e0c9477"},{"id":"31cda269bc","type":"paragraph","text":"三月四日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"289e0c9477"}],"page":{"id":"3486adf59f","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"289e0c9477","start":37,"end":37}}}},"__N_SSG":true}